author: Cory Olsen | colsen@mlive.com
title: Vote for coolest high school wrestling singlet in Michigan
text:
comments 
The top 10 has been announced in MLive's search for the coolest high school wrestling singlet in Michigan. 
Bay City Western, Cedar Springs, Clinton, East Kentwood, Grand Rapids Union, Jackson Northwest, Lakewood, Lapeer, Lowell and Midland will take to the mat...err...poll, to see which team has the coolest singlet. 
Preferences seem to be fairly equal when it comes to singlets. 
Whether it's flashy with plenty of graphics or simple with a single strong element, this group represents plenty of style. 
Voting will continue until Feb. 28 at 11:59 p.m. and the winner will be announced the morning of March 1.
